lead_paragraph: The Denver Broncos released three players who helped them win the Super Bowl: tight end Owen Daniels, guard Louis Vasquez, and long snapper Aaron Brewer.

headline.main: Broncos Release Daniels, Vasquez , Brewers to Free Cap Space
headline.print_headline: Broncos Release Daniels, Vasquez , Brewers to Free Cap Space
